parameters:
Memimi: Huh... Where are Orca Asparagus and Drillmaid? Don't
tell me those two slipped away from the party to go make out
somewhere...

Shark Broccoli: They probably still feel indebted to us,
offering to guard the venue... Should we call them over and
give them a beer lashing...

Orca Asparagus: Eeeeek... S-some scary folks have shown up!!
H-help me---!!!

Memimi: What's going on... Orca Asparagus? You and Drillmaid
are among the strongest monsters in the city... What's come
after you...?

Drillmaid: The monsters from the neighboring Unazushi City
have declared war...! Both Orca Asparagus and I were taken
down in one hit... They're monsters!! Even for the Shark
Duke...

Anomalocaris Mosman: Hey, hey... Unazushi City is rumored to
have worse public order than Doritoku City, a veritable slum
of monsters...!

Cerberus Octopus: They've come to capture us all in one fell
swoop, choosing this very moment to strike!! It's all
over... Uwaaaaah...!

Memimi: Calm down! Don't panic, you underlings...! You are
my subordinates, after all!!

Shark Broccoli: A monster capable of taking down Orca
Asparagus and Drillmaid in a single blow... Without a doubt,
this must be the strongest enemy we've faced. Shark Duke...
what shall we do?

Memimi: Fuhahahaha, it's decided! If they want to pick a
fight with us, then we'll just have to beat them at their
own game!! We'll fight no matter who the opponent is...
That's the rule of monsters!!

Memimi: Now, let's enjoy ourselves... It's been a while
since our last match! Everyone, watch closely... The battle
of the great leader, Shark Duke!!

Bunny-chan: Yes yes, all set♪ Let's get started tonight as
well... Monster Fight!!

The battle of the monsters, who live proudly in the
darkness, never ends...

Thank you for playing. This marks the beginning of the
epilogue.

In the epilogue, no events will occur, but you can walk
around the city after the ending. Also, a DVD that unlocks
all H events in the recollection room has been added.
We hope you enjoyed it to the end. A fine day for oily soba.

Memimi: Phew... The conflict with the monsters from Unazushi
City has come to a provisional end. It was a relief that
they were reasonable once we talked...

Memimi: Now that the cleanup is done, I think I'll spend
today just wandering around...
